text: Normani Kordei Hamilton ( ; born May 31, 1996) is an American singer, dancer and model. She auditioned on The X Factor as a soloist in 2012 after she became a member of pop girl group Fifth Harmony. ==References== Category:Singers from Atlanta Category:Living people Category:1996 births Category:American pop singers Category:American R&B; singers Category:American dancers
